0[2] "Product Information. Yescarta (axicabtagene ciloleucel)." Kite Pharma, Inc.  (2017):[3] "Product Information. Tecartus (brexucabtagene autoleucel)." Kite Pharma, Inc.  (2020):[4] "Product Information. Breyanzi (lisocabtagene maraleucel)." Bristol-Myers Squibb  (2021):[5] "Product Information. Abecma (idecabtagene vicleucel)." Celgene Corporation  (2021):', 1767369485);
